reviewText: I think it was a boy but when the movie was over I was totally certain.  He/she really acted more girly than I do and I'm certain I'm a girl.  This movie is very strangely done.  I was surprised when the end came, very little to indicate an ending.  English humor, low key and weird to an American.  Like nothing I've ever seen.  Not the best but not bad.  Funny in a way.  Confusing, too.
